	"keywords": "Google, Analytics, Search, Web Performance",
	"description": "If you are building products, you want to know how people are using the\nproducts, how they&#x27;re hearing about what you are building, and ultimately how\nthey reach you. The Search Console plays an important role in helping you track\nand measure these operational metrics.\n\nThe Console is free to use. You just have to prove to Google that you own a\nwebsite. Then Google will give you access to this treasure trove of search data.\n\nI am going to walk you through the Google Search Console’s core features",
