	"keywords": "Product Design, Writing Tips, Technical Writing, Writing, Design",
	"description": "In my time building and devising products – apps, websites, and graphics makers\n[http://gfxmaker.com/] – I have come across two types of people in general:\nthose that prefer qualitative narratives and those that prefer data and\nanalytics. \n\nThe first group is comfortable framing product development in the context of\nmore subjective user feedback and perspectives. The second group, wary of this\napproach, wants to apply “excel models” to work backwards from numbers. \n\nFor ease of categorization, l",
