	"keywords": "Product Design, Product Development, business strategy",
	"description": "When you&#x27;re building a product, there are different frameworks you can deploy to\nthink critically about what to build and why. These frameworks apply to business\nas well.\n\nWhen designing a product – or launching a startup – you should answer a few\nfundamental questions:\n\n 1. Should I enter the market or not?\n 2. Who else exists in this market and what are these firms doing or building?\n 3. What are the costs of entering this market? Are these costs fixed or\n    variable in nature?\n 4. If I decid",
