	"description": "Economics is the study of scarcity. It&#x27;s how people interact with value. \n\nEconomics gives you tools to understand how people produce, distribute, and\nconsume goods and services.\n\nBy applying economic theory, you can make well-reasoned business decisions. You\ncan better understand competitive forces.\n\nYou can also understand concepts like the “diamond-water paradox,” which\neconomist Adam Smith pondered but was ultimately unable to solve.\n\nIn this paradox, Smith struggled to explain why in this l",
